e to some extent.\n\n### Hiring for the Bar:\n- With the bar set to open, the narrator sought to hire bartenders not only with skill and experience but who also shared the vision for creative drinks with a classic twist.\n- An advertisement was posted on Craigslist which yielded numerous applications, including some inappropriate submissions.\n\nThis summary reflects the main themes and activities described in the text, centered on the establishment and conceptual development of a bar called Death & Company."
